definitions.definition: To fish with a squid fishhook.
To cause squidding ( an improper, partial, parachute inflation, that results in the sides of the parachute folding in on the center, and pulsating back and forth ) .

main_definition: ( fishing ) To fish with a squid fishhook.
secondary_definitions: ( parachuting ) To cause squidding ( an improper, partial, parachute inflation, that results in the sides of the parachute folding in on the center, and pulsating back and forth ) .
